name: Hacienda_Folding_Chair_2-Pack
reviews: Nice and sturdy, doesn't even look like a folding chair.

Nice, comfortable chairs. They do not fold very flat so storage was an issue but I'm not planning on folding them up. I use them at our vacation home in our small eating area and they are perfect. Will order more.
For the price and good for small spaces

I use them all over the house. I also got some with red seats. Very nice. They are extra seating to have on hand that you can put away when you don't want it. Quite sturdy and easy to fold and unfold.
Very comfortable, high quality, much better than a metal folding chair.
description:
Solid wood and veneer with Espresso finish. Padded faux leather seat available in Espresso, Red or Cream. Complements most any decor and folds for easy storage. Goes well with the Hacienda folding table.
